bring me the head of alfredo garcia ( spanish : tráiganme la cabeza de alfredo garcía ) is a 1974 american action film directed by sam peckinpah , co-written by peckinpah and gordon dawson based on a story by peckinpah and frank kowalski , and starring warren oates .   made in mexico on a low budget after the commercial failure of pat garrett and billy the kid ( 1973 ) , peckinpah claimed that , of all his films , alfredo garcía was the only one released as he had intended .   the film was a box office and critical failure at the time , but has gained a new following and stature in the decades since .